## 技术规格

### 技术栈

```typescript
{
  framework: 'Next.js 14',
  styling: 'Tailwind CSS + CSS Modules',
  animation: {
    complex: 'Framer Motion',
    simple: 'CSS Transitions'
  },
  fonts: {
    brand: 'Merriweather (衬线)',  // v11.0 更新
    body: 'Inter (无衬线)'
  },
  colors: 'PERMA 五色系',           // v11.0 更新
  performance: {
    bundle: '< 200KB',
    FCP: '< 1.5s',
    LCP: '< 2.5s'
  }
}
```

### 性能目标

| 指标 | 目标值 |
|------|--------|
| Lighthouse Performance | > 90 |
| Lighthouse Accessibility | > 95 |
| 首屏加载时间 (3G) | < 2s |
| 动画帧率 | 60fps |
| Bundle Size | < 200KB |

